results.description:
If you need to check your sound, take a look at this useful tool! Sound Check app is designed to generate sound with various frequency, from very low to very high. With this helpful utility you can easily check the sound quality of your headphones or just make some noise!

The main features of Sound Check app:
- a wide range of available wave frequency;
- 4 types of waves to choose from: sine, saw-tooth, triangle, and plane;
- a handy generator of different sounds and noises.

This app can be a checking tool for any headphones you're about to buy but want to test the quality of sound right off the bat, or a cool app for everyone who loves to tinker with sounds, sound waves, and sound effects!

